arStrings.szText: Confront the {c_highlight}Infernal Hordes{/c} again by finding more {c_highlight}Infernal Compasses{/c}.

{c_highlight}Infernal Compasses {/c}can be found in{icon:Marker_Helltide,2.5}{c_highlight}Helltide{/c},{icon:Marker_NightmareDungeonEntrance,2.5}{c_highlight}Nightmare Dungeons{/c}, and{icon:Marker_Pit,2.5}{c_highlight}The Pit{/c}.
{c_highlight}Infernal Compasses{/c} will scale with your Torment level.
